	Support for relocatable installation.
	* configure.ac: Invoke AC_RELOCATABLE, AC_REPLACE_FUNCS([memmove]),
	gl_FUNC_STRERROR, gl_XREADLINK, gl_CANONICALIZE.
	* INSTALL: Document --enable-relocatable and --with-libintl-prefix.

